leted normally, and there are no new failures to report. The pipeline remains healthy, so I'm staying silent on this one.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Comparing current state (06:51 UTC) vs. heartbeat-state.json baseline (06:46 UTC):\\n\\n| Session | 06:46 | 06:51 | Δ |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p) | running ✅ | running ✅ | — (child sessions spawned, normal cycle) |\\n| `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p) | running ✅ | running ✅ | — |\\n| `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status) | running ✅ | running ✅ | — (child b4b417fc: aborted, normal lifecycle) |\\n| `telegram:direct:6053576134` (Lead) | running ✅ | **done** ✅ | completed normally |\\n| `telegram:group:-5163901258` | idle ✅ | idle ✅ | — |\\n\\n**Changes:** Lead direct session completed normally (expected lifecycle after Daily Briefing work done). No new failures. No blockers. No new sessions. All cron monitors healthy.\\n\\nPipeline stable. **Silent.**\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 20599,\n            \"output\": 684,\n            \"totalTokens\": 35636,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 409,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776235933089,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e689e16fec98bebd5b9f2379d0cd6\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"8284d65a\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\"