n migration\" — whether they're asking about the v4 infrastructure setup status or something else entirely."},{"type":"text","text":"## V4 Ecosystem Migration — Status\n\n**Tổng quan:**\n\n| Hạng mục | Trạng thái |\n|---|---|\n| 34 agent workspaces | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| Presence system | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| SKILL_GATES / DEV_GATE | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| HANDOVER / FEEDBACK templates | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| Ecosystem backup | ✅ (2026-04-11) |\n| GIT_WORKFLOW.md | ✅ Hoàn tất |\n| **17 commits chưa push** | ⚠️ Cần push lên origin/main |\n\n**Chưa xong / Cần dọn dẹp:**\n- Project repos (`ahv-qlhv-be`, `ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-dtlx-backend`) nằm trong workspace v4-ecosystem-review — không đúng chỗ\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup` — cần review xem có phải migration script chính thức không\n- ops-manager: đã xóa nhưng chưa commit cleanup\n\n**Cần Lead xác nhận:** \"Plan migration\" ở đây là migration gì?\n1. **V4 infrastructure** → ✅ gần xong, cần push 17 commits + dọn repo\n2. **Migration script (ahv-openclaw-setup)** → đọc nội dung rồi báo cáo\n3. **Khác** → nói rõ hơn\n\nChờ Lead hướng dẫn tiếp."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":477,"output":565,"totalTokens":24430,"cacheRead":22455,"cacheWrite":933,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776226552335,"responseId":"062e43f9b5eb94d8ca5013359b1987c9","__openclaw":{"id":"6d34c150","seq":12}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776208566543,"sessionId":"26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":21354,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me read the full 2