l need to be sent via a different mechanism (e.g., a dedicated Telegram bot runner, a cron/macro that calls the Telegram API directly, or a parent agent with the appropriate tool)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":336,"output":448,"totalTokens":11706,"cacheRead":7447,"cacheWrite":3475,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776184845234,"responseId":"062da10dffbe4344ad63a1cddfb9e551","__openclaw":{"id":"8eaf43c5","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776184692752,"sessionId":"2514861e-9ccc-41ee-8f48-1e19d13c0819","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":11075,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776184464031,"endedAt":1776184688954,"runtimeMs":16394,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/2514861e-9ccc-41ee-8f48-1e19d13c0819.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to send a message to a Telegram group. Let me use the message tool to send this exact message to the Telegram group -5163901258.\n\nLooking at the available tools, I don't see a direct \"message\" tool for Telegram. Let me check the available functions... I see there are tools for confluence, gitlab, stitch, etc. but no direct Telegram messaging tool listed.\n\nWait, let me re-read the tools. There's no `message` tool visible in my tool list. The tools available are:\n- read, edit, write, exec\n- process\n- sessions_list, sessions_history, s